added.title: Small
added.description: Mao Mao's legendary, gigantic and critical father visits his son at his new job as sheriff.

added.title: Legend of Torbaclaun
added.description: When the Sweetypies think the mythical Torbaclaun has come to Pure Heart Valley, Mao Mao tries to prove to them that it isn't real.

added.title: Meet Tanya Keys
added.description: When bounty hunter Tanya Keys comes to town for Badgerclops, it's up to Mao Mao and Adorabat to save their friend -- even if he's been on the wrong side of the law.

added.title: Weapon of Choice
added.description: Worried that his sword is a glorified consolation prize, Mao Mao sets out to prove the worth of his weapon.

added.title: Roundabout Part 1
added.description: Forever Knight finally assembles his Round Table of young but super-powerful Knights, including— Ben?! With Ben's help, Forever Knight leads his new minions in an all-out attack on a Particle Accelerator - his true intention to transform it into a Time Machine and conquer history!

added.title: Roundabout Part 2
added.description: Forever Knight, with an over-clocked Time Machine in his grasp and a group of super- baddies by his side, is close to conquering all of history, but a certain hero with a team of 10 aliens on his side has other plans— foiling Forever Knight at every twist and turn in time!

added.title: #DCSuperHeroBoys Part 1
added.description: What begins as a simple vandalism investigation becomes an all-out turf war when the team encounters a powerful trio of Kryptonians bent on world domination, and, perhaps even worse, a rival team of SUPER HERO BOYS!

added.title: #DCSuperHeroBoys Part 2
added.description: What begins as a simple vandalism investigation becomes an all-out turf war when the team encounters a powerful trio of Kryptonians bent on world domination, and, perhaps even worse, a rival team of SUPER HERO BOYS!

added.title: Bad Moon Rising Part 1
added.description: Starscream makes a play for leadership of the Deceptions as the Autobots storm the Decepticon's Moon Base.

added.title: Bad Moon Rising Part 2
added.description: The Autobots work to stop the Moon from crashing into the Earth as Starscream must reckon with betraying Megatron.

added.title: A Devil on Your Shoulder/Vestral Visions
added.description: A Devil on Your Shoulder: Near giving up, Magnus gains new strength and insight on the AO's mission to find Core Cells that will eventually lead him down a dark hole./Vestral Visions: Drago's sickness leads Dan to a revelation that there is an ailing Core Cell and if they can't find a cure, the planet itself may falter.

added.title: Bakuzoned!/The Golden Secret
added.description: Bakuzoned!: Strata's return is much more than a simple rematch when he's been infected by a strange ooze and the AO are in danger of the same fate./The Golden Secret: Using Strata's gauntlet, the AO think they've found a way through the labyrinth, but soon discover trusting the enemy is not always best.

added.title: The Bakugan Breakers/The Awful Ones
added.description: The Bakugan Breakers: Magnus's new team of Bakugan Brawlers overhear Lightning's warnings of a sick Core Cell and decide to capture the dog to find its location./The Awful Ones: Magnus heads into the Labyrinth to claim the Fortus Core Cell for his own, but comes in direct contact with the evil versions of the AO.

added.title: The Mask of Pride/The Graveyard of Courage
added.description: The Mask of Pride: Driven by revenge, Magnus decides to go back into the labyrinth, face the AO and claim the Fortus Core Cell energy for himself./The Graveyard of Courage: Super charged by the Fortus Core Cell, Magnus wages war on the AO only to discover his newfound power has a price attached.

added.title: Vestroia
added.description: Vestroia, Part 1: The AO discover the only way to stop Magnus, and possibly save him, involves shutting down the infected Fortus Core Cell./Vestroia, Part 2: The AO must decide whether or not to help Benton Dusk destroy the infected Fortus Core Cell, risking the destruction of their own Bakugan.

added.title: Too Much/Who Are You?
added.description: Too Much: The Hide Matrix goes crazy and a simple AO training mission turns into a complicated rampage that brings down Studio D./Who Are You?: After the loss of their HQ, the AO is a little off, but in talking to Benton Dusk, they learn a new sense of purpose for their team.

added.title: Bakugan: Beyond the Brawl - BBG Tug-O-Brawl, Part 1
added.description: It all comes down to this, a "no rules" tug of war for the Bakugames crown!

added.title: Bakugan: Beyond the Brawl - BBG The Epic Elimination
added.description: In the thrilling conclusion to the first Bakugames' event, not only is the winner determined, but also which Bakugan Faction is eliminated from the competition!

added.title: Bakugan: Beyond the Brawl - BBG Begins!
added.description: The opening event of the Bakugames comes with a surprise twist for all the Factions.

added.title: Bakugan: Beyond the Brawl - BBG Sky Brawl
added.description: Bakugame Brawling takes on a whole new dimension in the preliminary showdowns high above Dan's backyard.

added.title: Bakugan: Beyond the Brawl - BBG Lights Out Sumo Brawl for it All
added.description: Skill and strategy may not be the only factors in determining the winner of this Sumo-style Bakugames' Brawl.

added.title: Bakugan: Beyond the Brawl - BBG Joust Brawling
added.description: Factions square off in a series of medieval inspired jousts with skateboards and Power Calls subbing for horses and lances.

added.title: Bakugan: Beyond the Brawl - BBG Bakutoss
added.description: Factions use creative ways to hurl a member of their own squad the greatest distance!

added.title: Bakugan: Beyond the Brawl - BBG Brawling Along
added.description: Bakugan Factions must pull out all the stops to avoid elimination as the "Keep the Brawl Rolling" challenge continues.

added.title: Bakugan: Beyond the Brawl - A Cure for Hiccups
added.description: When Artulean's prank on Howlkor causes him to laugh so hard he gets the hiccups, the Bakugan hound exacts his revenge with some questionable "cures" on his Darkus kin.

added.title: Bakugan: Beyond the Brawl - Bakucore Brawl
added.description: When the music stops, the Brawls begin for these Bakugan.

added.title: Bakugan: Beyond the Brawl - BBG Tug-O-Brawl, Part 2
added.description: The thrilling finale decides which Faction will be crowned the Bakugames Champion.

added.title: Bakugan: Beyond the Brawl - BBG Sky Brawl Finals
added.description: One Bakuan Faction uses less than honorable tactics to secure a victory in this lofty challenge.

added.title: Dia del Trabajo
added.description: Llegó el Día del Trabajo, y Robin les enseña a los demás Titanes la importancia del trabajo.

added.title: Titanes Clasicos
added.description: Para demostrar su punto de vista sobre los dibujos animados clásicos de superhéroes, iControl Freak envía a los Titanes a una versión antigua de Jóvenes Titanes en Acción!

added.title: Trono de Huesos
added.description: Cuando los demás Titanes comienzan a escuchar música heavy metal, Robin les advierte sobre los peligros.
